g-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#inclass_recovery_network_%e2%80%93_giai_phap_phuc_hoi_he_thong_chuyen_biet_cho_phong_may_tinh_tap_trung\" >Inclass Recovery Network \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh t\u1eadp trung<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#quan_ly_tap_trung_%e2%80%93_uu_the_vuot_troi_cua_ban_network\" >Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1eadp trung \u2013 \u01afu th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n Network<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#trien_khai_linh_hoat_qua_mang_lanwan\" >Tri\u1ec3n khai linh ho\u1ea1t qua m\u1ea1ng LAN\/WAN<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#tiet_kiem_thoi_gian_va_chi_phi_bao_tri\" >Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#phu_hop_cho_phong_may_quy_mo_lon\" >Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#tinh_nang_noi_bat_cua_inclass_recovery_network\" >T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Inclass Recovery Network<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#doi_tuong_su_dung_ly_tuong\" >\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-inclass-recovery-network\/#tong_ket\" >T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"inclass_recovery_network_%e2%80%93_giai_phap_phuc_hoi_he_thong_chuyen_biet_cho_phong_may_tinh_tap_trung\"><\/span>Inclass Recovery Network \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh t\u1eadp trung<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Inclass Recovery Standalone l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c m\u00e1y t\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb, th\u00ec Inclass Recovery Network l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho\u00a0<em>h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i m\u1ea1ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9<\/em>\u00a0\u2013 nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o CNTT.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-2\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quan_ly_tap_trung_%e2%80%93_uu_the_vuot_troi_cua_ban_network\"><\/span>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1eadp trung \u2013 \u01afu th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n Network<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n Standalone ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ee5c b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean t\u1eebng m\u00e1y, Inclass Recovery Network cho ph\u00e9p qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y tr\u1ea1m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 trung t\u00e2m. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m, kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh, ho\u1eb7c gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi v\u00e0i thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-3\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"trien_khai_linh_hoat_qua_mang_lanwan\"><\/span>Tri\u1ec3n khai linh ho\u1ea1t qua m\u1ea1ng LAN\/WAN<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Inclass Recovery Network \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea1ng LAN ho\u1eb7c WAN, cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y c\u00f9ng l\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Standalone kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n do gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf m\u1ee9c m\u00e1y c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-4\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tiet_kiem_thoi_gian_va_chi_phi_bao_tri\"><\/span>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 CNTT nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng m\u00e1y c\u00e0i l\u1ea1i h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh hay ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 khi d\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n Standalone.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-5\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu_hop_cho_phong_may_quy_mo_lon\"><\/span>Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ebfu Inclass Recovery Standalone l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t, th\u00ec phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Network l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y t\u00ednh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng tin h\u1ecdc, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n, hay c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng CNTT.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-6\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tinh_nang_noi_bat_cua_inclass_recovery_network\"><\/span>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Inclass Recovery Network<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i<\/li>\n<li>\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1eeb m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 trung t\u00e2m<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng m\u00e1y tr\u1ea1m t\u1eeb xa<\/li>\n<li>T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 LAN\/WAN<\/li>\n<li>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian tri\u1ec3n khai<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec5m m\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9c<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-7\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi_tuong_su_dung_ly_tuong\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc, trung t\u00e2m tin h\u1ecdc<\/li>\n<li>Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc s\u1ed1<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh d\u00f9ng chung t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-8\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong_ket\"><\/span>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Inclass Recovery Network kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u2013 m\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1y th\u00f4ng minh, gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n d\u1eef li\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<div id=\"genai-translator-shadow-root\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<ul>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y tr\u1ea1m t\u1eeb m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nhanh sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i<\/li>\n<li>Tri\u1ec3n khai \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t qua m\u1ea1ng LAN ho\u1eb7c WAN<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m t\u1eeb xa d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"genai-translator-shadow-root\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":16965,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[246,332],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-16964","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-phan-mem-inclass","7":"product_cat-phan-mem-quan-ly-tap-trung-va-sao-luu-du-lieu","9":"first","10":"instock","11":"shipping-taxable","12":"purchasable","13":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/16964",